Frusenholm

A town tucked along one of the many roads. The mountains behind this town sing with the laborers of Frusenholm's work songs echo along the base. Many people come here to trade songs and goods.

Frusenholm is a location that can be found in the Jarvonia region.

Faction

Frusenholm is a member of the following factions:

Jarvonia
